《'''穷查理宝典'''》（{{lang-en|''Poor Charlie's Almanack''}}）是美国投资家[[查理·芒格|查理·芒格]]的演讲稿和谈话集，由彼得·考夫曼编纂。简体中文译本译者是李继宏。第一版在2005年出版，第三版在2008年出版。

==内容梗概==
查理·芒格是[[波克夏·哈薩威公司|伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司]]长期任职的副董事长。《穷查理宝典》集中了他的投资思想，而不是他那句名言“我没有什么要补充的”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/michaelsimmons/2015/03/23/how-one-life-hack-from-a-self-made-billionaire-leads-to-exceptional-success/|title=How One Life Hack From A Self-Made Billionaire Leads To Exceptional Success|last=Simmons|first=Michael|website=Forbes|language=en|accessdate=2020-09-02|date=2019-02-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fool.com/investing/general/2015/01/31/charlie-munger-5-quotes-show-why-warren-buffetts-2.aspx|title=Charlie Munger: 5 Quotes Show Why Warren Buffett's No. 2 is More Important Than You Think -|last=Hall|first=Jason|date=2015-01-31|website=The Motley Fool|language=en|accessdate=2020-09-02}}</ref>

查理·芒格是[[本杰明·富兰克林|本杰明·富兰克林]]的崇拜者，这本书的书名取自本杰明·富兰克林《[[窮理查的年鑑|穷理查的年鉴]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/charlie-munger-investing-wisdom-at-berkshire-hathaway-meeting-2017-5|title=CHARLIE MUNGER: 'A lot of other people are trying to be brilliant. We're just trying to be rational.'|last=Holodny|first=Elena|website=Business Insider|date=2019-02-16|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gurufocus.com/news/606331/charlie-munger-an-intellectual-who-found-success-in-investing|title=Charlie Munger: An Intellectual Who Found Success in Investing - GuruFocus.com|website=www.gurufocus.com|date=2019-02-16|language=en}}</ref>

《穷查理宝典》的净收入捐给了[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣玛利诺_(加利福尼亚州)|圣马力诺]][[漢庭頓圖書館|亨廷顿图书馆]]的芒格研究中心。<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.poorcharliesalmanack.com/ | title= Poor Charlie's Almanack and Seeking Wisdom - Official Website of PCA Publications | publisher= poorcharliesalmanack.com | date= 2010-09-28 | language= en | accessdate= 2020-09-02 | archive-date= 2011-02-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110217171322/http://www.poorcharliesalmanack.com/seekingwisdom.html | dead-url= yes }}</ref>

